==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
A quote from the [[wikipedia:Analects_of_Confucius|Analects of Confucius]].

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén ér wú xìn, bù zhī qí kĕ

===Phrase===
'''[[人]][[而]][[无]][[信]]，[[不]][[知]][[其]][[可]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') If a man has no honesty, I do not know what he would be suitable for.

===Alternate forms===
[[人]][[而]][[無]][[信]]，[[不]][[知]][[其]][[可]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

